### LOCI : skeleton + dispatcher (stub ENOSYS) — Sprint 34y

#### Added
- **Module `src/io/loci.c` + `include/io/loci.h`** : émulation de
  l'interface LOCI (Lovely Oric Computer Interface, sodiumlb 2024).
- **Décodeur bus MIA $03A0-$03BF** : register file 32 octets,
  routage R/W intégré au callback I/O principal.
- **Dispatcher 36 API ops** (0x01-0x05, 0x0F-0x12, 0x14-0x1C, 0x80-0x83,
